{"tid":376587,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲人喺咪唔識「可圈可點」點用？","createTime":"2017-08-27T06:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T03:36:51.000Z","uid":10392,"like":367,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e316e86a94f6777854549d752b57109fb645b044","tid":376587,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"這個成語是指古人看文章的時候, <br />\n如果看見有一些精彩的字句, <br />\n就會用紅筆在字句的傍邊加上一點或一個小圓圈。 <br />\n<br />\n因為在字傍加上「圈」及「點」, <br />\n所以這個成語就叫做「可圈可點」。 <br />\n<br />\n現在,形容別人「可圈可點」, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就是讚美別人的的字句</span>。<br />\n<br />\n原指文章中有精妙的句子，有值得欣賞、值得讚美的地方。現使用範圍擴大，常用於文藝體育類的新聞報導，又進而擴大到其他領域，<span style=\"color: red;\">形容或稱讚一切出色、精彩、值得稱道的事物</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見班on9 10個有9個用錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9649d781acc2b5d305caba567ea57fedb92cc74","tid":376587,"uid":60151,"like":249,"dislike":5,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"呢篇文章可圈可點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93f5e2433c087352e2790edaaf9146b9cb5a355","tid":376587,"uid":100623,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"係 好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為自己好醒識用 我又唔好意思話佢"},{"pid":"d1ecc38bf3d094fa7aee1d467b8b4e7b78d5eb4d","tid":376587,"uid":27458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"咁多人用錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac617b95745aff59abd924a97c06639345748c","tid":376587,"uid":26249,"like":304,"dislike":9,"score":295,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"我就係個個on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以為係指 可讚可彈<br />\n長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60981dcfc1b1ca7debea050a75b36ae99f6d1d42","tid":376587,"uid":53682,"like":270,"dislike":5,"scor