"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f943e5cb852cfcc9d544905f990cfd5cb3c071","tid":376587,"uid":106503,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學已經聽老師咁講<br />\n成班人講錯時，佢重係唔係錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n言語係生唔係死，好多時都係靠約定俗成。就算知道可圈可點原意係代表好，正常都唔會讚人果陣話人地可圈可點。因為口語就係要簡便，最緊要大家都get，何需故意斟酌。<br />\n<br />\n不過要寫正式文稿，eg新聞、講稿既人就要識同埋避免用呢d原意跟約定俗成有衝突既語句。因為假如你用果陣係跟原意，受眾會覺得兀突；假如你係跟約定俗成既意思，人地又會話你冇學識。"},{"pid":"616f575b65e22ed8bdf294a7f896a4cb8e766c55","tid":376587,"uid":30519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"笑貧不笑娼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ac6a92767e366a62ddab94bd2266077c85844c","tid":376587,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/175350_d8aac971b803f92cd0760e905e44b421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F175350_d8aac971b803f92cd0760e905e44b421.jpg&h=b6f6fce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/240860?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/240860?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"5b3483a72c0d53877da42bc867cd6c8f71c68283","tid":376587,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/175350_d8aac971b803f92cd0760e905e44b421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F175350_d8aac971b803f92cd0760e905e44b421.jpg&h=b6f6fce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/240860?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/240860?ref=ios</a></blockquote><br />\n可以照用真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"2b1cfc9d88f632d3bfc416d5080fe3932cf7d43f","tid":376587,"uid":28477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小學已經聽老師咁講<br />\n成班人講錯時，佢重係唔係錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n言語係生唔係死，好多時都係靠約定俗成。就算知道可圈可點原意係代表好，正常都唔會讚人果陣話人地可圈可點。因為口語就係要簡便，最緊要大家都get，何需故意斟酌。<br />\n<br />\n不過要寫正式文稿，eg新聞、講稿既人就要識同埋避免用呢d原意跟約定俗成有衝突既語句。因為假如你用果陣係跟原意，受眾會覺得兀突；假如你係跟約定俗成既意思，人地又會話你冇學識。</blockquote><br />\n認同，所以可以取代情況下寧願用其他詞代替就算，費事認定話你又要解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時點樣令大眾普遍易明都係一種學問，而且亦都俾一味追求原義黎得重要<br />\n<br />\n唔係再發展落去就會好似何文匯一味推崇古音咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e2de296ae47e33802a6342eeda5e56d8128afe","tid":376587,"uid":18030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"唔該，我想讀翻書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05133ed2e259dabb3bb3b7baf2a661e73ec3ab9a","tid":376587,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:33:00.000Z","msg":"係以前有個古人係張紙到畫左個好細既圓圈，旁邊d人睇唔清以為係一點<br />\n意思係一件事可圈可點=由唔同角度睇有唔同意思咁解"},{"pid":"005a22638ad0d8504615984931a9c5a3ff06eb2e","tid":376587,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係以前有個古人係張紙到畫左個好細既圓圈，旁邊d人睇唔清以為係一點<br />\n意思係一件事可圈可點=由唔同角度睇有唔同意思咁解</blockquote><br />\n呢個解法唔知邊度走出嚟<br />\n但真係好多人都咁解<br />\n結果 可圈可點 就等如 見仁見智"},{"pid":"254fe692961d1853a3bba9c59f52e65ebf7b465f","tid":376587,"uid":53389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"上下其手都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人成日以為係指摸人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522c6ff6435dd0d544dcf1258afa9041f8fee809","tid":376587,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s